# ShakuAPI

A lightweight Python SDK for interacting with **Shaku REST APIs**, including:

- OAuth token management (access, refresh, revoke)
- Size measurement
- Clothes recognition
- Garment measurement

## Installation
```bash
pip install shakuapi


